Class Thing

java.lang.Object
  Thing
Direct Known Subclasses:
Character, MoneyBullet
public class Thing
extends java.lang.Object

Thing represents all the objects within the game such as characters, items, and obstacles.

Author:
John Kim, Tanner Lai, Raymond Zhao
